extends layoutBS

block content
  .body
    header#home.w3-display-container.w3-content.w3-wide(style = "max-width: 1500px")
      img.w3-image(src = "../images/bg3.jpg" alt = "home" width = "1500" height = "800")  
      .w3-display-middle.w3-margin-top.w3-center
        br
        br
        br
        br 
        br
        br
        h1.w3-xxlarge.w3-text-white
          span.w3-padding.w3-black.w3-opacity-min
            b S O N
          br
          br
          span.w3-hide-small.w3-text-light-grey Social Organizer Networking
          br
          br
          br
          br
    div#about.w3-container(style = "padding: 128px 16px")
      h3.w3-center ABOUT THE APP
      p.w3-center.w3-large Key features of our APP
      .w3-row-padding.w3-center(style = "margin-top:64px")
        .w3-quarter
          i.fa.fa-calendar.w3-margin-bottom.w3-jumbo.w3.center
          p.w3-large Calendar
          p Manage schedules in Calendar. Try to add events by pressing "add calendar" and edit it by clicking the event. You can see events in your list. Don't forget to our voice functions. 
        .w3-quarter
          i.fa.fa-group.w3-margin-bottom.w3-jumbo.w3.center
          p.w3-large Friends
          p Share your schedules with your friends. Use our secret checking to see who can do brunch on Saturday at 9:30? Share SON to your friends and take advantage of SON together.   
        .w3-quarter
          i.fa.fa-bullhorn.w3-margin-bottom.w3-jumbo.w3.center
          p.w3-large Notifications
          p Get notifications of your upcoming events in time. You can also manage your friend requests and invitaions here. Add more friends, accept your friends' invitations and have a nice day. 
        .w3-quarter
          i.fa.fa-cog.w3-margin-bottom.w3-jumbo.w3.center
          p.w3-large Settings
          P Give yourself a cool username and complete your personal information here. Your friends can see your profile! Customize everything to your fav taste. SON is your secretary. 
    div.w3-container.w3-light-grey(style = "padding: 128px 16px")
      .w3-row-padding
        .w3-col.m6
          h1.w3-jumbo
            b SON 
          h1.w3-xxxlarge.w3-text-grey
            b Why use it? 
          p
            span.w3-large Your life is never easier. 
              | SON is a convenient voice enabled reminder app with networking functions. 
              | SON is your personal secretary. It manages all your events and reminds you upcoming events in time. 
              | It can also send your schedule to your friends or invitate available friends to attend events.
              | SON improves your working effciency, keeps your life organized, and connects you with your friends. 
              | With SON, you will never forget one single thing. With SON, you will never feel boring.
        .w3-col.m6
          img.w3-image.w3-right.w3-hide-small(src = "../images/home1.jpg" width = "450" height = "550" )
          .w3-center.w3-hide-large.w3-hide-medium
            button.w3-button.w3-block.w3-padding-large(onclick = "document.getElementById('download').style.display='none'")  
            img.w3-image.w3-margin-top(src = "../images/home1.jpg" width = "335" height = "471" )
    div#team.w3-container.w3-padding-64.w3-center(style = "padding: 128px 16px")     
      h2.w3-text-black OUR TEAM
      p The ones who creates SON
      br
      br
      .row
        .col-1
        .col-2
          img.w3-circle.w3-hover-opacity(src = "../images/port4.jpg" alt = "Xuantong" style = "width45%")
          h3.w3-text-dark-grey Xuantong Liu 
          p Developer
        .col-2
        .col-2
          img.w3-circle.w3-hover-opacity(src = "../images/port5.jpg" alt = "Yushan" style = "width45%")
          h3.w3-text-dark-grey Yushan Wang
          p Developer
        .col-2
        .col-2
          img.w3-circle.w3-hover-opacity(src = "../images/port6.jpeg" alt = "Ziqing" style = "width45%")
          h3.w3-text-dark-grey Ziqing Huang
          p Developer
        .col-1
    div.w3-container.w3-light-grey
      #contact.w3-container.w3-content.w3-padding-64(style="max-width:800px")
      h2.w3-wide.w3-center CONTACT
      p.w3-opacity.w3-center
        i Lets get in touch. Send us a message 
      .w3-row.w3-padding-32
        .w3-col.m6.w3-large.w3-margin-bottom
          i.fa.fa-map-marker(style="width:30px")
          |  Waltham, MA
          br
          i.fa.fa-phone(style="width:30px")
          |  Phone: (781) 736-5333
          br
          i.fa.fa-envelope(style="width:30px")  
          |  Email: lxt@brandeis.edu
          br
        .w3-col.m6
          form(action="/action_page.php" target="_blank")
            .w3-row-padding(style="margin:0 -16px 8px -16px")
              .w3-half
                input.w3-input.w3-border(type="text" placeholder="Name" required="" name="Name")
              .w3-half
                input.w3-input.w3-border(type="text" placeholder="Email" required="" name="Email")
            input.w3-input.w3-border(type="text" placeholder="Message" required="" name="Message")
            button.w3-button.w3-black.w3-section.w3-right(type="submit") SEND
    footer.w3-container.w3-padding-32.w3-center.w3-black(style = "padding: 128px px")
      h4 Follow Us
      .row
      a.w3-button.w3-large.w3-teal(href="javascript:void(0)" title="Facebook")
        i.fa.fa-facebook 
      | 
